trans-unit.target: Converte objetos para os valores de modelo.

trans-unit.source: This class is used in `PropertyGrid` scenarios to convert an object into a `ModelItem`.
trans-unit.target: Esta classe é utilizada na `PropertyGrid` cenários para converter um objeto para uma `ModelItem`.

trans-unit.source: It converts from a `ModelPropertyEntry` to the `ModelItem` that owns the property.
trans-unit.target: -Converte a partir de um `ModelPropertyEntry` para o `ModelItem` que possui a propriedade.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Converters.ObjectToModelValueConverter"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Cria uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Converters.ObjectToModelValueConverter"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Converts the specified <xref uid="langword_csharp_ModelPropertyEntry" name="ModelPropertyEntry" href=""></xref> to a <xref uid="langword_csharp_ModelItem" name="ModelItem" href=""></xref> that contains the original entry.
trans-unit.target: Converte especificado <xref uid="langword_csharp_ModelPropertyEntry" name="ModelPropertyEntry" href=""> </xref> para um <xref uid="langword_csharp_ModelItem" name="ModelItem" href=""> </xref> que contém a entrada original.

trans-unit.source: This method is a two-way binding with the `PropertyValue` object.
trans-unit.target: Este método é um enlace bidirecional com o `PropertyValue` objeto.

trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_ModelPropertyEntry" name="ModelPropertyEntry" href=""></xref> to convert.
Converts the specified <xref uid="langword_csharp_ModelItem" name="ModelItem" href=""></xref> to a <xref uid="langword_csharp_ModelPropertyEntry" name="ModelPropertyEntry" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Converte especificado <xref uid="langword_csharp_ModelItem" name="ModelItem" href=""> </xref> para um <xref uid="langword_csharp_ModelPropertyEntry" name="ModelPropertyEntry" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This method is a one-way binding with the `ModelPropertyEntry`.
trans-unit.target: Este método é um enlace unidirecional com o `ModelPropertyEntry`.

trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_ModelItem" name="ModelItem" href=""></xref> to convert.
Returns a <xref:System.Object> that contains the converted <xref uid="langword_csharp_ModelPropertyEntry" name="ModelPropertyEntry" href=""></xref>..
trans-unit.target: Devolve um <xref:System.Object>que contém o convertida <xref uid="langword_csharp_ModelPropertyEntry" name="ModelPropertyEntry" href=""> </xref>…</xref:System.Object>
